# DiskWise macOS — Architecture & Conventions

DiskWise is an **AI storage consultant** for macOS — not just a treemap viewer. It scans drives, detects duplicates (including video fingerprinting), classifies storage, and recommends safe cleanup actions.

**Canonical docs:** `README.md`, `docs/architecture.md`, `docs/database.md`, `docs/local-development.md`.

## Repository layout

```
diskwise-macos/
├── app/DiskWise/           # SwiftUI desktop app
├── Sources/                # Swift packages (kits)
│   ├── DatabaseKit/
│   ├── DiskScannerKit/
